{{Infobox language |name=Undu |nativename= |states= |region=[[Benishangul-Gumuz]] |ethnicity=[[Berta people]] |speakers=? |familycolor=Nilo-Saharan |fam2=[[Berta languages|Berta]] |iso3= |glotto=undu1236 |glottorefname=Undu }}
'''Undu''' is an erstwhile dialect of [[Berta language|Berta]] that is distinct enough to be considered a separate language.
